WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.536
Shah Rukh Khan: Can you tell me
what the world-famous scientist Albert Einstein

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:11.490
and an average student from a small house
in Vadodra could have in common?

00:00:11.490 --> 00:00:15.520
Well, they both loved star gazing!

00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:18.039
Dr. Karan Jani, would also 
not count the stars,

00:00:18.039 --> 00:00:23.260
but keep looking for answers
to the mysteries hidden inside them

00:00:23.710 --> 00:00:28.220
Today some answers to those
mysteries he will share with us.

